{"word":"G5500 - χειροτονέω - cheirotonéō - khi-rot-on-eh'-o - Choose","slug":"G5500","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χειροτονέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>cheirotonéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khi-rot-on-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Choose"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C7;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - cheirotoneo&#x0304;</b> - <i>khi-rot-on-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5495\">G5495</a> and <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>teino&#x0304;</b> (to <i>stretch</i>); to be a <i>hand reacher</i> or <i>voter</i> (by raising the hand), that is, (genitive) to <i>select</i> or <i>appoint:</i> - choose, ordain."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5495\">G5495</a>, <a href=\"#/G5496\">G5496</a>, <a href=\"#/G5497\">G5497</a>, <a href=\"#/G5498\">G5498</a>, <a href=\"#/G5499\">G5499</a>, <a href=\"#/G886\">G886</a>"}]}